column5: Have you seen the commercial of the 3 buddys meeting to go fishing, they all buy coffees for each other, well next time you see it, check out the boat tied to the dock.with just the motor on the back, the whole front end is out of the water  no way those 3 guys would be able to fish in that at the same time.
and i thought you were going to say how they show up with 9 coffee's and when they get to the dock , they only have 1 coffee each.
I just hope they have a pee bucket... don' t want them drowning after all that liquid input!
Empty Timmies cups make a great little pee bucket....just make sure you get an X-large!!
good one never even saw that
